                    <span>Paris, France</span>
                </footer>
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote class="testimonial-card" role="listitem">
                <div class="testimonial-stars" aria-label="5 star rating">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"Green Oasis connected us with the most breathtaking casino resort in Santorini. The caldera views, the entertainment, the suites — an absolutely surreal premium experience from start to finish."</p>
                <footer>
                    <strong>James &amp; Clara M.</strong>
                    <span>London, UK</span>
                </footer>
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote class="testimonial-card" role="listitem">
