                <p>"The Algarve cliffside resort was unlike anything we've experienced. Seamless booking, truly luxurious VIP accommodation, world-class entertainment, and staff who anticipated every need. Exceptional."</p>
                <footer>
                    <strong>María R.</strong>
                    <span>Madrid, Spain</span>
                </footer>
            </blockquote>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt" aria-label="Call to action">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-box">
            <div class="cta-badge" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="section-label-gold">Start Your Journey</span>
            <h2>#1 Casino Resort Platform — Exclusive Stay &amp; Play Experience 2026</h2>
            <p>Ready to experience the world's finest casino resort destinations? Our VIP hospitality specialists are on hand to craft your perfect resort stay — from arrival to checkout, every moment perfected. Premium Resort &amp; Entertainment Platform.</p>
            <div class="cta-actions">
                <a class="btn btn-accent btn-lg" asp-action="Contact">
                    Reserve Your Stay
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M1 8a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h11.793l-3.147-3.146a.5.5 0 0 1 .708-.708l4 4a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-4 4a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L13.293 8.5H1.5A.5.5 0 0 1 1 8z"/></svg>
                </a>
                <a class="btn btn-outline-light" asp-action="About">Learn About Us</a>
            </div>
            <p class="cta-microcopy">
                <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="#10B981" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2H4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v7a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h8a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V7a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-1V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/></svg>
                Instant reservation · No booking fees · Secure &amp; private · 18+ Entertainment only
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
